  "keyFeatures": [
    "Non-custodial 2-of-3 Shamir secret sharing — private keys never stored whole on any server",
    "Multi-chain support: EVM, Solana, Tron, Bitcoin, Cardano, and XRP",
    "Multisig vault creation, activation, and lifecycle management per chain",
    "Multi-step order workflows: create, sign (threshold), execute, and reject",
    "Organization B2B features: team wallets, vault provisioning, spending limits, and audit logs",
    "Address book with Force Address Book enforcement and memo/destination-tag support",
    "Portfolio and balance tracking across all supported chains",
    "TypeScript-first SDK with OPRF-based wallet-password sessions and async context helpers"
  ],
